                        <label>lasgun (Locke pattern carbine)</label>
                    </value>
                </li>

                <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
                    <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="OGI_Gun_LasGun_Locke"]/description</xpath>
                    <value>
                        <description>The Lascarbine is a carbine form of the standard Imperial Lasgun that is easier to carry and to aim that its larger counterpart. It will often possess a folding stock to further optimise its size. However, as a result of these modificatios, a Lascarbine has a shorter effective range and will fire fewer shots before depleting its power pack when compared to the standard Lasgun.\n\nThe Locke Pattern Lascarbine is a lighter, cut down variant of the Lascarbie which is commonly issued to Planetary Defence Force regimets and local militias of the Astra Militarum.</description>
                    </value>
                </li>

<!--  ==============================================================================================================  -->
<!--     + ALL CASES (cont)                                                                                           -->
<!--  ==============================================================================================================  -->
<!--       + For OGI_Gun_LasGun_Catachan REPLACE label                                                                -->
<!--                                        WITH label lasgun (Catachan pattern carbine)                              -->
