                        <label>lasgun (Voss pattern carbine)</label>
                    </value>
                </li>

                <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
                    <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="OGI_Gun_LasGun_Voss"]/description</xpath>
                    <value>
                        <description>The Lascarbine is a carbine form of the standard Imperial Lasgun that is easier to carry and to aim that its larger counterpart. It will often possess a folding stock to further optimise its size. However, as a result of these modificatios, a Lascarbine has a shorter effective range and will fire fewer shots before depleting its power pack when compared to the standard Lasgun.\n\nWhile technically a Lascarbine, the Voss Pattern Lasgun is the standard weapon issued to the Steel Legion regiments of the Astra Militrarum raised from Armageddon (known during the Heresy-era, and prior to its relocation, as Ullanor).</description>
                    </value>
                </li>

<!--  ==============================================================================================================  -->
<!--     + ALL CASES (cont)                                                                                           -->
<!--  ==============================================================================================================  -->
<!--       + For OGI_Gun_LasGun_Lucius REPLACE label                                                                  -->
<!--                                      WITH label lasgun (Lucius pattern)                                          -->
<!--       + For OGI_Gun_LasGun_Lucius UPDATE description                                                             -->
<!--  ==============================================================================================================  -->
